      <title>鲍威尔讲话前，服务业指数疲软，阻止债券抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bond-selloff-halted-by-weak-services-gauge-before-powell-speaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于服务业活动指标弱于预期，增强了人们对美联储本月将降息的预期，美国国债抛售势头停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bond-selloff-halted-by-weak-services-gauge-before-powell-speaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:00:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国关闭俄罗斯加密货币富豪网络，转移寡头数十亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方表示，他们已经关闭了俄罗斯网络，该网络通过在欧洲、中东和南美洲交换现金和加密货币，为寡头、街头帮派和间谍转移数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行通胀斗争即将结束但尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-s-lagarde-sees-weaker-economic-growth-and-uncertain-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行抗击通胀的斗争已接近尾声，但尚未获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-s-lagarde-sees-weaker-economic-growth-and-uncertain-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 13:44:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨瓦德尔在英国 Cerberus 房地产纠纷案中胜诉，获赔 3.58 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/sabadell-wins-358-million-in-uk-property-dispute-with-cerberus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨瓦德尔银行 (Banco Sabadell SA) 赢得了针对 Cerberus Capital Management LP 的诉讼，该诉讼涉及一项与西班牙房地产资产相关的交易，并从伦敦法官那里获得 3.58 亿欧元（3.765 亿美元）的赔偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/sabadell-wins-358-million-in-uk-property-dispute-with-cerberus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币价格接近 96,000 美元，加密货币等待特朗普的下一步行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bitcoin-btc-churns-near-96-000-as-crypto-awaits-trump-s-next-step</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币投机者将比特币的价格保持在 100,000 美元的里程碑水平，以期美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普采取进一步措施支持该行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bitcoin-btc-churns-near-96-000-as-crypto-awaits-trump-s-next-step</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 00:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
