      <title>OPEC+ 协议取得进展和伊朗制裁后油价保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在周二上涨后保持稳定，OPEC+在维持供应关闭协议方面取得进展，吸引算法交易员重返市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-4</guid>
