    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔讲话前几小时，科技股受提振：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大科技公司的股价上涨推动股市上涨，交易员们仔细研究最新的经济数据，等待杰罗姆·鲍威尔的讲话，以寻找美联储下一步行动的线索。美国国债和美元波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>星巴克能够自救吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/can-starbucks-save-itself-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[价格上涨和等待时间延长导致星巴克顾客减少。由于销售额连续三个季度下降，咖啡师不得不应对无休止的定制选择，这家陷入困境的连锁店需要重新开始。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/can-starbucks-save-itself-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 17:01:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
